This gorgeous nameplate comes with a 14" (child), 16", or 18" inch solid sterling silver box chain attached to both sides, included in the low price! You choose 3 names. Up to 8 letters each.... each name with one capital letter!! Solid Sterling Silver, Standard size name necklace, Capital letter 4.0 cm wide , 1.2 mm upgraded nameplate thickness. All names made with the print font shown in the photograph of this item. All items made and shipped out within 4 business days! These are not stock items!
